WITH "CTE_Cash_Discounts" AS (
    SELECT 
        "ReceivableItem"."ID"                       AS "ID",
        "ReceivableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate1"     AS "CashDiscountDueDate",
        "ReceivableItem"."CashDiscountPercentage1"  AS "CashDiscountPercentage"
    FROM "o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem"
    WHERE "ReceivableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate1" IS NOT NULL
    UNION ALL 
    SELECT 
        "ReceivableItem"."ID"                       AS "ID",
        "ReceivableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate2"     AS "CashDiscountDueDate",
        "ReceivableItem"."CashDiscountPercentage2"  AS "CashDiscountPercentage"
    FROM "o_custom_ReceivableItem" AS "ReceivableItem"
    WHERE "ReceivableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate2" IS NOT NULL
),
    "CTE_DiscTerms_Order" AS (
    SELECT 
        "Cash_Discounts"."ID"                                               AS "ID",
        "Cash_Discounts"."CashDiscountDueDate"                              AS "CashDiscountDueDate",
        "Cash_Discounts"."CashDiscountPercentage"                           AS "CashDiscountPercentage",
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "Cash_Discounts"."ID"
        ORDER BY "Cash_Discounts"."CashDiscountPercentage")                 AS "DiscountTermOrder"
    FROM "CTE_Cash_Discounts" AS "Cash_Discounts"
)                        
SELECT 
    'CashDiscountDueDate' || '::' || "CashDiscountTerms"."ID" || '::' || "CashDiscountTerms". "DiscountTermOrder"       AS "ID",
    "CashDiscountTerms"."ID"                                                                                            AS "ReceivableItem",
    "CashDiscountTerms"."CashDiscountDueDate"                                                                           AS "Time",
    "CashDiscountTerms"."DiscountTermOrder"                                                                             AS "DiscountTermOrder",
    "CashDiscountTerms"."CashDiscountPercentage"                                                                        AS "CashDiscountPercentage"
FROM "CTE_DiscTerms_Order" AS "CashDiscountTerms"
